com.dhemery.victor.discovery

Class IosSdk

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dhemery.victor.discovery.IosSdk

  • public class IosSdk
extends Object
    Represents an iOS SDK in the currently active Xcode development environment. The active development environment is the one reported by xcode-select -print-path.

      • simulatorBinaryPath

        public String simulatorBinaryPath()

        Compute the path to the iPhoneSimulator Simulator executable in the active development environment.

        WARNING. This method:

        • Assumes that the simulator executable is located at a fixed location within the iPhone Simulator platform.
        • Does not determine whether a file exists at that location, or that the file is executable.
        Returns:
        the absolute path to the iPhoneSimulator Simulator executable in the active development environment.
